            <bioghist>
                <p>Records of Smith Funeral Home of West Chester, PA.</p>
            </bioghist>

            <scopecontent>
                <p>Includes 9 volumes of funeral registers for 1905-1907, 1913-1946. Also 3 ledgers
                    for 1887-1912, State Board of Undertakers Lincenses certificates for Wm. B.
                    Smith 1906, Joseph B. Smith 1906 and Ashton Buchanan Talbot Smith 1925. Framed
                    commission of Joseph B. Smith as Coroner of Chester County, 1872 (OV, stored
                    separately on shelf)</p>
            </scopecontent>


            <accessrestrict>
                <p>The collection is open for research.</p>
